window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Summon. Scry. Spin, spiral, and sweep. Learn how to bend time, draw down the moon's energy, and use mirror magick. Whether novice or adept, a Witch's world is filled with wonder and magick. It's also filled with the hard work and dedication to learning that are part of living the Craft every day. </p> <p>Silver RavenWolf presents a fascinating introduction to the Craft in <i>To Ride a Silver Broomstick</i>. This indispensable guide presents tried-and-true Witch wisdom, dished out with Silver's down-to-earth warmth and humor. You'll learn the essentials of Witchcraft, including webweaving; astral projection, bi-location, and power animals; stocking your magickal cabinet; cleansing, consecrating, and charging; healing techniques; telepathy, psychometry, and mind power; and color, candle, and sympathetic magick. </p>"; 
